</div>
<ol start="1">
<li><a href="http://www.clearance-comet.co.uk/kitchen-home/fridges-freezers.html">Comet Clearance</a> o<span style="color: #333333;">ffers an auction system, which allows you to place bids on all sorts of items including fridges and freezers. If you’re looking to buy on this site it might be worth watching a few items first. See what sort of price they go for so you can gauge if you are getting the best deal. If you’re lucky enough to buy on a quiet day you may pick up a real barging. It&#8217;s worth noting that loads of their stock is brand new to so it&#8217;s a great place to pick up a bargain!</span></li>
<li><a href="http://www.argos.co.uk/static/Browse/ID72/14418615/c_1/2%7Ccategory_root%7CKitchen+and+laundry%7C14418476/c_2/3%7Ccat_14418476%7CFridge+freezers%7C14418615/r_001/1%7CPrice+Cut%7CYes%7C1.htm">Argos Clearance</a><span style="color: #333333;"> has a wide variety of items at discounted prices. You can get up to a third off fridges and fridge freezers. It is remember that discounted items are not covered by the 30 Day Money Back Guarantee. They also offer finance but bare in mind if you to take out finance you may pay a fair bit more in the long run once interested has been accounted for.</span></li>
<li><a href="http://search.debenhamsplus.com/refrigeration/page.asp">Debenhams Sale</a><span style="color: #333333;">. Debenhams are currently offering a clearance sale to get rid of stock. There are some very nice fridges, including designer makes. All at discounted prices. Worth taking a look while you can!</span></li>
</ol>
